Cell["\<\
As the vector in question is separable, the Schmidt rank must be 1; that is, \
there is only one non-zero Schmidt number.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1619579837,ExpressionUUID->"b6df1953-c080-4acf-9cad-ad4f30371ced"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

